    <item>
      <title>南非拖欠电力的市政当局欠 Eskom 45 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-s-delinquent-municipalities-owe-eskom-4-5-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非各市政府共计欠 Eskom Holdings SOC Ltd. 823 亿兰特（45 亿美元）的欠款，陷入困境的这家国有电力公司正在努力收回这些欠款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-06/south-africa-s-delinquent-municipalities-owe-eskom-4-5-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 10:12:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
